      "source": [
        "## 🔢 Step 6 — Embed Chunks & Store in ChromaDB\n",
        "\n",
        "We use HuggingFace's `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` — a small, fast, FREE embedding model.\n",
        "\n",
        "⚠️ This cell may take 2-3 minutes on first run (downloads the embedding model)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 27,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 243,
          "referenced_widgets": [
